PG APIs
Retrieve available PG places in a specific city

URL: http://localhost:8085/pg/{city}

Method: GET

Example:

Code
GET http://localhost:8085/pg/Bangalore
List out available PG places in a specific locality

URL: http://localhost:8085/pg/locality/{locality}

Method: GET

Example:

Code
GET http://localhost:8085/pg/locality/BTM
Retrieve a specific PG place detail by id

URL: http://localhost:8085/pg/details/{id}

Method: GET

Example:

Code
GET http://localhost:8085/pg/details/1
Retrieve the owner details of a specific PG

URL: http://localhost:8085/pg/owner/{id}

Method: GET

Example:

Code
GET http://localhost:8085/pg/owner/1
üîπ Owner APIs
Add a new PG place

URL: http://localhost:8085/owner/places/add/{ownerId}

Method: POST

Request Body (JSON):

json
{
  "registrationNumber": "PG123",
  "builtUpArea": 1200,
  "rent": 8000,
  "city": "Bangalore",
  "locality": "BTM",
  "available": true
}
Retrieve all PG places added by the owner

URL: http://localhost:8085/owner/places/{ownerId}

Method: GET

Example:

Code
GET http://localhost:8085/owner/places/1
Change the status of PG place (Available or Not Available)

URL: http://localhost:8085/owner/places/{id}

Method: PUT

Example:

Code
PUT http://localhost:8085/owner/places/1
Edit Place details

